title: Classical Performance - Atlanta Guitar Trio - January 23, 2015
teaser: The Atlanta Guitar Trio is in town for a performance in Bradenton, but they stop by our Sarasota Performance and Broadcast Studio first, to play for you live on the radio! Join Bethany Cagle as she welcomes the Trio for some great classical guitar arrangements.  The Atlanta Guitar Trio live on Classical WSMR.
